{
  "stem": "21013.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would say starting in 1935 I noticed that among my friends there was whispering.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were wearing white stockings and blue cornflowers, which was the sign of National Socialism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you could tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were all kinds of underground movements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it-- it was clear to me as a child of 14 or 13 that it wasn't going to be long before Hitler would get into Austria.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my father was in total denial.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a synagogue in the 10th district and it was called the [INAUDIBLE] Temple.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think the name of the rabbi was Mandel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grammar school was very close to our house and it was an easy walk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very happy at school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no other Jewish children in that-- in my class at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but grammar school was only four years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After four years, you went either to a public high school, which was four years, or to a semi-public high school, which was then eight years.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was called gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for that, the parents had to pay, very little but they had to pay.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went to what was called a realgymnasium, which specialized in mathematics, geometry, and was really for engineers, which was not my forte particularly, because I was much more artistic than mathematically inclined.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a long streetcar ride, three streetcars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At the age of 10, I had to go into what was then considered bad traffic and changed streetcars three times to go to school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's how far away it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were two other Jewish girls in my class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the professors were very strict and there was a lot of homework.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think I enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
